                <h3 class="font-semibold">What are some current trends in men's fashion?</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">Current trends in men's fashion include oversized silhouettes, retro-inspired pieces like Hawaiian shirts, and sustainable fashion choices such as organic fabrics and upcycled garments.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold">How can I accessorize to enhance my outfit?</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-gray-600">Accessorize your outfit with statement watches, stylish belts, and quality leather bags. Don't forget about classic sunglasses and subtle jewelry pieces to complete your look.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

